Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared to die, then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride... on a sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoooa! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Rocketman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even allow passengers to be on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it. I've finished servicing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water and coal have been loaded\Nand it's storing the steam right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were getting it ready for us, pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait to rejoice until you survive the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this was a failure built\Nbefore Puffing Tom was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you tune it up,\Nits steam engine can't control the speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thanks, Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... take us with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Bro, Franky, was taken\Nin by the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go after them... but we can't\Nget through Aqua Laguna by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to save Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're deeply indebted to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... pirates! \NDon't go getting thrown off, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now departing Water Seven for Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the sea train Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go...! \NTo get everything back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:25.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:28.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:32.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:40.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:50.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:57.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:04.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:11.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:15.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:19.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:23.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:34.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:45.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:57.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:15.03,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Rescue Our Friends! A Bond\NAmong Foes Sworn with Fists!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming out at a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an underground canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got some water in my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gonna happen when you stand out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I didn't see that coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey, monster granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't we falling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is real close now. \NWe'll keep on going and go down in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The sea train has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Now we're gonna charge forth, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump! Sodom! Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping us,\Nthe entire Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the connection cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those must be the highest-grade bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! \NDon't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheerful bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, monster granny! \NIs this as fast as it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fast at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it gets on the railway, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Railway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's drifted quite a ways away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've observed the sea train\N since its development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent message from the engine room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train will get on the railway shortly.\NOnce it does, it'll rapidly accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight to something so\Nthat your injuries won't be severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll get injured regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! I missed it. \NBut I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! A little to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it next... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Gonbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and\Ncome inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay! We're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec, okay?\NI'll stop the train right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brake doesn't work on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Hm? What the heck?\NThat kinda looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Straw Hat brother! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Hurry and get\NChimney and Gonbe inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get on the railway,\Nthey'll be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! All right! They got on the railway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Hey! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from Kokoro-san! \NShe's something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I was afraid of\Nwhat was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, indeed. \NThat's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those high waves, it must've\Nbeen hard to find the railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, indeed.\N You're exactly righ... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, indeed, indeed. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, she's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We definitely have to let Iceberg-san know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. \NI-I'm sure he's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, indeed. Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I bet he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about a guy who\Nsurvived being hit by a sea train...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know... that the violent\Ndisciple of Tom, Cutty Flam, died?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hit by the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first disciple of Tom,\Nthe world's greatest shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do it... I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro-san, let's drink\Ntogether one of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when we have something to drink to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san... please just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect... everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town... and these blueprints as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(447,447)}"Four years later"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you'd know who if I tell you "Cutty Flam."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show him in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turn him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a roundabout way of meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... anyway, what's up with\Nthat funny looking body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Since my whole\Nbody came to be of no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rebuilt my body using \Niron scraps and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your company contracts to\Nbuild ships for the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna tolerate you doing\Nthings that help the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Tom-san and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who made the weapons\Nthat caused the incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have things you wanna say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't think that I've forgiven\Nyou in the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you had the nerve\Nto show your face after what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely thought that you were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since the Government told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Tom-san forgave you,\NI'm not going to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What the hell are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these the blueprints we\Nsaw for that ancient weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use the name Cutty Flam from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government couldn't\Nget this out of Tom-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before I get targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island with them... Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam from Tom's Workers is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't use that name,\Nthere'll be no connection between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, if you leave the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blueprints' whereabouts\Nwill vanish into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if they come after you\Nwhen you don't have them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said what I came to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to end up like Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the blueprints with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by any chance, you find that your\Nlife is in danger, just hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna do that, then you\Ncan even burn them before their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were me, would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san achieved so many great things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he gave up everything in order to\Npreserve these blueprints for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, as long as there's a risk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a woman named Nico Robin\Ncan restore the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world needs those blueprints to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue to keep them with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I am to be killed...\NI won't give them to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may build this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't my giving them\Nto you answer that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet face to face,\Nwe yell at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you... and you\Nmay feel the same about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...glad that... you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stupid-berg! \NI'm not gonna leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I wanna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do what you \Ntell me to, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Moron-ky! Why don't\Nyou get what I'm saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is in order to protect the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's you who's not getting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna leave no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Why am I remembering\Nhim at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that idiot... Iceberg... doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously! \NGeez, I told you, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you'd get blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that acceleration sure was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Geez...\N--Yeah, really, that scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my lower back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are weird guys in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:18:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to go with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried\Nto stop you, you didn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy you'd go this far\Nto rescue your friend from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is also the culprit who tried to kill Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, there are lots of\Nthings that I wanna say to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie! We're not gonna\Nlet you steal all the glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that we'd be able to find\NIceberg-san's assassins if we followed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we hid in the tender together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... it seems we were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us join you guys in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the foes you're gonna get revenge\Non took Big Bro Franky as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! And we clearly know who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna take responsibility \Nif something happens to Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's Iceberg-san\Nwho's endured the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie! First, explain it to us! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the true culprit, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not that dense.\N We have a rough idea as to who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could guess if they\Nsuddenly disappeared for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll tell you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true identities of those masked men are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lucci, Kaku, Kalifa and Blueno from the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was them who tried to kill Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You never even guessed that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you said they went\Nback to their hometowns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they, during an emergency like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it was Michael and\NHoichael from the backstreets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You don't know them?!\NThey're famous in the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!\NTo start with, you guys are--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Boy, I ate a lot.\N I'm finally full.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we got in fights back in\Ntown with both the Franky Family
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Galley-La shipwrights,\Nwe're all going after the same enemy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest one among the guys\Nwe're gonna fight is that pigeon guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine. I'm definitely gonna beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is a battle to get back\Nwhat those four took from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, if we don't\Nreach them, nothing will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Grandma! Grandma! \NIt's Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's already here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro-san! Is it okay for you to leave\Nthe engine room at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We somehow need to dodge that high wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?\NThat we can't control Rocketman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we want to operate it,\Nnothing works, including the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job ended when the train got on the railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the train is always\Nrunning at full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do anything, the train will\Ncrash into the big wave! Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we have the same goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's senseless to fight separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. We're comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends are also in\Nthe train that left before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fighting force will still increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't let that big wave beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all achieve our goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:19.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:24.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:32.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:41.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:50.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:23:00.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! That wave is really huge! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! If we don't do something,\Nit'll collide with Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's do it, shall we, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--What're you guys gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fire a cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smash the Wave! Luffy and Zoro\NUse the Strongest Combo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
